  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "`base_reward(state, index)` depends on validator's balance in that `state` so if we update validator's balance during each step we will get different `base_reward(state, index)` in each step.\r\nIf we bookkeeping the rewards/penalties for each validator and only update validator's balance at the end, the `base_reward(state, index)` will be the same throughout.",
